---
import AudioPlayer from "../../components/AudioPlayer";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  return [{ params: { exercice: "z" } }];
}
---

<Layout title="Fonemas">
  <article class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <section class="mt-10">
      <button class="underline sm:text-lg text-xl lg:text-2xl"> Letras </button>
    </section>
    <section class="mt-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/svg/z/Fonema_Z.svg"
          alt="Fonema Z"
          class="col-start-1 col-span-3 my-auto"
        />
        <div class="col-start-7 col-span-6 my-auto">
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-4xl sm:col-span-6">
            La <span class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]">letra z</span> se pronuncia
            siempre como la letra s en castellano.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto">
        <p
          class="text-lg text-center max-sm:mx-auto sm:text-xl lg:text-3xl sm:col-span-6 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-8 max-w-[90%] sm:max-w-[100%]"
        >
          Es decir, siempre pronunciamos como la <span class="text-bold"
            >letra s</span
          > las palabras escritas con las <span class="text-bold"
            >letras s y <span class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span>.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-16">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-3 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto"
      >
        <div class="col-start-3 col-span-8 my-auto">
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-3xl text-center">
            Pensemos <span class="text-bold">por ejemplo</span> en la pronunciación
            de:
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/images/svg/z/Zona.svg"
          alt="Imagen de globo terraqueo"
          class="lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-3 mx-auto"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/svg/z/Sana.svg"
          alt="Imagen de una persona"
          class="lg:col-start-8 lg:col-span-3 mx-auto"
        />
        <span
          class="col-start-3 col-span-3 text-6xl text-bold text-[#6610F2] text-center my-10"
        >
          Zona
          <AudioPlayer
            audio_path={"/audio/z/Zona.mp3"}
            className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-5 mx-auto"
            client:load
          />
        </span>

        <span
          class="col-start-8 col-span-3 text-6xl text-bold text-[#6610F2] text-center my-10"
        >
          Sana
          <AudioPlayer
            audio_path={"/audio/z/Sana.mp3"}
            className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-5 mx-auto"
            client:load
          />
        </span>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "En ingles" -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-2 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Mano_Derecha.svg"
          alt="Imagen de una mano apuntando a la derecha"
          class="lg:col-start-1 lg:col-span-2 my-auto"
        />
        <div class="col-start-3 col-span-8">
          <p class="lg:text-3xl sm:text-2xl text-center mx-5 mb-10">
            Tal como lo puedes notar, cuando pronunciamos las <span
              class="text-bold"
              >letras s y <span class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span>
            </span>, no hacemos <span class="text-bold"
              >ninguna diferencia entre ambas.</span
            >
          </p>

          <p class="text-3xl text-center mx-10">
            De hecho, bien podriamos escribir <span class="text-bold">
              s o <span class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span>, pero las pronunciamos
              igual:
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <span
          class="col-start-3 col-span-3 text-6xl text-bold text-center mt-20"
        >
          <span class="text-[#6610F2]">S</span>ona
          <AudioPlayer
            audio_path={"/audio/z/Zona.mp3"}
            className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-5 mx-auto"
            client:load
          />
        </span>
        <span
          class="col-start-8 col-span-3 text-6xl text-bold text-center mt-20"
        >
          <span class="text-[#6610F2]">Z</span>ana
          <AudioPlayer
            audio_path={"/audio/z/Sana.mp3"}
            className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-5 mx-auto"
            client:load
          />
        </span>
        <p
          class="col-start-2 col-span-10 text-3xl text-center mt-20 mb-10 mx-auto w-[85%]"
        >
          Aunque sabríamos que la <span class="text-bold"
            >ortografía no es la correcta</span
          >, en nuestras mentes seguiríamos pensando en una <span
            class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]">zona</span
          > geográfica y en una persona <span class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]"
            >sana</span
          >.
        </p>
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Estrella.svg"
          alt="Imagen de una estrella."
          class="lg:col-start-2 lg:col-span-3"
        />
        <p class="lg:col-start-6 lg:col-span-7 lg:text-3xl my-auto text-right">
          En inglés, las <span class="text-bold"
            >letras s y <span class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span>
          </span> al inicio de una palabra tienen <span class="text-bold">
            pronunciaciones distintas y significados distintos.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Por ejemplo" -->
    <section class="mb-12 sm:mb-24">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-3xl text-bold text-center">Por ejemplo:</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <img
              src="/images/svg/z/Sip.svg"
              alt="Sip"
              class="w-54 h-72 max-w-[70%] -mb-16 sm:max-w-[100%] sm:-mb-8"
            />
            <p
              class="text-[#6610F2] text-4xl sm:text-6xl text-extrabold mb-2 sm:mb-8"
            >
              Sip
            </p>
            <span class="text-bold text-4xl">(beber un sorbo)</span>
            <AudioPlayer
              audio_path={"/audio/z/Sip.mp3"}
              className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-10"
              client:load
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <img
              src="/images/svg/z/Zip.svg"
              alt="Zip"
              class="w-54 h-72 max-w-[70%] -mb-16 xl:max-w-[100%] rotate-[17.53deg] origin-center
                                                                    tranform -translate-x-4 min-[350px]:-translate-x-2 sm:-mb-8"
            />
            <p
              class="text-[#6610F2] text-4xl sm:text-6xl text-extrabold mb-2 sm:mb-8"
            >
              Zip
            </p>
            <span class="text-bold text-4xl">(subir el cierre)</span>
            <AudioPlayer
              audio_path={"/audio/z/Zip.mp3"}
              className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 mt-10"
              client:load
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Ejercicios de percepción" -->
    <section>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-2 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto"
      >
        <div class="col-start-1 col-span-8 sm:col-span-8 mb-12 mr-20">
          <p class="text-3xl sm:text-2xl text-left">
            Una forma de hacernos conscientes de las
            <span class="text-bold lg:block"
              >diferencias entre la escritura y la pronunciación
            </span> del castellano y del inglés es hacer
            <span class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]"
              >ejercicios de discriminación</span
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-start-2 col-span-4 row-start-2 flex justify-center items-center transform -translate-y-24 -translate-x-6 sm:-translate-y-20 sm:translate-x-0"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/svg/global/Flecha.svg"
            alt="Flecha"
            class="w-24 h-24 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 rotate-[5.53deg]"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-end-13 col-span-9 max-w-[97%] ml-auto sm:max-w-[100%] sm:col-end-13 sm:col-span-7 row-start-2 transform -translate-y-4"
        >
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-right leading-[1.45rem]">
            Los <span class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]"
              >ejercicios de discriminación</span
            > permiten que podamos
            <span class="text-bold">diferencias la pronunciación</span> de una letra
            de otra y, además, nos ayudan a mejorar nuestra <span
              class="text-bold">escritura en la lengua extranjera.</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Pronuncia las siguientes palabras" -->
    <section class="mb-20 sm:mb-24">
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-lg sm:text-2xl text-center mb-24 max-w-[70%] sm:max-w-[40%] mx-auto leading-[1.45rem]"
      >
        Utiliza la siguente lista para hacer un <span
          class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">ejercicio de discriminación</span
        > de las <span class="text-bold"
          >letras s y <span class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span>
        </span>
      </p>

      <div
        class="relative w-full max-w-[350px] sm:max-w-[650px] mx-auto py-32 sm:py-16"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Superior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Superior"
          class="w-full transform -translate-y-48 sm:-translate-y-36"
        />

        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-50">
          <div class="w-full px-24 transform translate-y-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 gap-x-32 sm:gap-x-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zoom
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zoom.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Seven
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Seven.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zone
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zone.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Sister
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Sister.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zebra
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zebra.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Sorry
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Sorry.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Inferior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Inferior"
          class="w-full transform translate-y-40 sm:translate-y-28 z-0"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Como podemos pronunciar el fonema" -->
    <section class="-mb-32 c400:-mb-44 xl:-mb-48">
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-3xl text-bold text-center mb-16 max-w-[80%] mx-auto leading-[1.45rem]"
      >
        ¿Cómo podemos<span class="text-[#6610F2]"> pronunciar z</span>
        en inglés?
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto">
        <div
          class="col-start-1 col-span-12 -mb-16 sm:col-start-1 sm:col-span-7 sm:mb-16 xl:col-span-7 xl:mb-8"
        >
          <p class="text-3xl sm:text-2xl text-left leading-[1.45rem]">
            Partimos <span class="text-bold"
              >pronunciando la letra s en castellano.</span
            >
            Luego, mientras estamos pronunciando la <span class="text-bold"
              >letra s,</span
            > ponemos dos dedos sobre nuestra garagnta e <span class="text-bold"
              >imitamos el zumbido de una abeja.</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-start-7 col-span-5 sm:col-start-8 sm:col-span-4 flex justify-center items-center"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/svg/global/Nota_Musical.svg"
            alt="Nota Musical"
            class="w-40 h-40 transform sm:rotate-[0deg] rotate-[31.53deg] translate-y-2 min-[350]:translate-x-8 sm:-translate-y-6 translate-x-4"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-end-13 col-span-12 ml-auto sm:col-end-13 sm:col-span-7 transform -translate-y-8 sm:translate-y-4"
        >
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-right leading-[1.45rem]">
            <span class="text-bold"
              >Si vibra la garganta, estás pronunciando la <span
                class="text-[#6610F2]">letra z</span
              >;
            </span>si no vibra como el zumbida de una abeja, estás pronunciando
            la <span class="text-bold">letra s</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-start-1 col-span-7 flex justify-center items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/png/abeja.png"
            alt="Abeja"
            class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 transform -translate-y-32 -translate-x-4 c400:-translate-y-44
                                                                        c550:-translate-y-52 c550:-translate-x-20 sm:-translate-y-48 sm:-translate-x-12"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="mt-10">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-2 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto"
      >
        <video
          src="/videos/z/Muestra_Vibracion_S.mkv"
          controls
          muted
          class="col-start-1 col-span-6 mx-auto"
        >
          Tu navegador no admite el elemento <code>video</code>.
        </video>
        <video
          src="/videos/z/Muestra_Vibracion_Z.mkv"
          controls
          muted
          class="col-start-7 col-span-6 mx-auto"
        >
          Tu navegador no admite el elemento <code>video</code>.
        </video>
        <span
          class="col-start-2 col-span-4 text-center text-6xl text-extrabold text-[#6610F2] my-auto"
          >Letra s</span
        >
        <span
          class="col-start-8 col-span-4 text-center text-6xl text-extrabold text-[#6610F2] my-auto"
          >Letra z</span
        >
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Pronuncia las siguientes palabras" -->
    <section class="mb-80">
      <p
        class="text-3xl sm:text-2xl text-center mb-80 max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[43%] mx-auto leading-[1.45rem]"
      >
        Ahora, pon tu mano sobre tu garganta y sin escuchar los audios, <span
          class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]"
          ><br class="hidden min-[400px]:block max-[450px]:block" /> pronuncia las
          siguientes palabras:</span
        >
      </p>

      <div
        class="relative w-full max-w-[350px] sm:max-w-[650px] mx-auto py-32 sm:py-16"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Superior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Superior"
          class="w-full transform -translate-y-48 sm:-translate-y-80"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-50">
          <div class="w-full px-24 transform translate-y-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-20">
              <img
                src="/images/svg/z/Sin_Voz.svg"
                alt="Imagen que representa una persona con la boca cerrada"
              />
              <img
                src="/images/svg/z/Con_Voz.svg"
                alt="Imagen que representa a una persona hablando"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 gap-x-32 sm:gap-x-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Silent
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Silent.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zap
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zap.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Singer
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Singer.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zombie
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zombie.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Summer
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Summer.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zinc
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zinc.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Inferior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Inferior"
          class="w-full transform translate-y-40 sm:translate-y-72 z-0"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "¿Quieres seguir ejercitando?" -->
    <section>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center relative">
        <div class="col-span-2 text-center">
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-3xl text-center mb-4 sm:mb-12">
            <span class="text-mediumbold">¿Quieres seguir </span><span
              class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]"
            >
              ejercitando</span
            ><span class="text-mediumbold">?</span>
          </p>
          <nav
            class="transform transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-110"
          >
            <a
              href="/exercise/z"
              class="text-[#6610F2] text-extrabold text-2xl sm:text-4xl w-full cursor-pointer px-4 text-center inline-flex justify-center"
            >
              Haz click aquí
            </a>
            <img
              src="/images/svg/global/Destacado.svg"
              alt="Destacado"
              class="mx-auto w-20 sm:w-40 sm:mt-2"
            />
          </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="col-start-2 col-span-2 -mt-12 sm:-mt-14">
          <img
            src="/images/svg/global/Mano_Izquierda.svg"
            alt="Mano Izquierda"
            class="w-32 h-32 sm:w-56 sm:h-56 transform translate-y-2 translate-x-14 sm:-translate-y-8 sm:translate-x-32"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
